Package kr.ac.konkuk.ccslab.cm.manager Description

The manager package contains classes that provides various CM services that are not in the CM stub package.

Other CM classes or applications can use this package by selecting a suitable class and by calling a method according to the requester's purpose.

Author:
CCSLab, Konkuk University
